<p><strong>Problem Statement: </strong> You are given the head of a singly linked-list. The list can be represented as:
<br>
L0 → L1 → … → Ln - 1 → Ln <br>
Reorder the list to be on the following form:
<br>
L0 → Ln → L1 → Ln - 1 → L2 → Ln - 2 → …<br>
You may not modify the values in the list's nodes. Only nodes themselves may be changed.</p>


